g.title: _P_Main_Connecting_TryingConnect->_P_Main_Connecting_Initial
g.text: after(5 s)/add_message("unable to connect to server " + get_server(curr_server),"info")⁏ if (not reconnecting) [[curr_server = (curr_server + 1) % get_nr_of_servers()⁏ ]]⁏

g.title: _P_Main_Connecting_Initial->_P_Main_Connecting_TryingConnect
g.text: after(100 ms)/add_message("trying to connect to server " + get_server(curr_server),"info") ^network.connect
